{"tid":1740340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明送頭行動本大回報低","createTime":"2019-11-20T01:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:45:47.000Z","uid":62011,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"69cdd1c5b0ac7fd5e3696c7977ae2dc25bbc7b0b","tid":1740340,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"啲黎明行動係推遲咗港豬返工，唔係阻擋到港豬返工。港豬返工既決心係大到你估唔到。你堵路佢哋落車清路障，你塞港鐵會有班藍絲廢老出嚟指責，最慘冇人幫口幫手，仲要引埋幫狗入嚟，連累其他學生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔否認係有小小作用，令到某啲站大排長龍。但最終效果係去唔到個目標，而且會陰啲陰啲咁送頭。<br />\n<br />\n如果係咁既情況，不如諗下停止/重新思考其他方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad63b0289bbda6fec44ef239934e2934a38813","tid":1740340,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:58:31.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得勇武暫時要休息，咁作為和理非嘅你請今晚出場，今晚有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"870f54529c916c2d783f2fa2ee409ad5dc7799cf","tid":1740340,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33c8ca6046424df2a02df46f3c155f4299fdfb79","tid":1740340,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f746bb7bfcae6439441f6f7d3eb2e6ec4c86b6","tid":1740340,"uid":162272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:05:23.000Z","msg":"我公司啲人 今日最多都係遲一個鐘返到。"},{"pid":"62e12eed5f35d6c28b7642ca1ec0cbd5325c5dfb","tid":1740340,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"減低公司人手 變相減低公司收入"},{"pid":"0d3572184533306a31ba8f94d201d28c451756f2","tid":1740340,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2